Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, y'all wanna hear something amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.54,0:00:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this time it's for sure seriously amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how amazing is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The twin brothers inside a kangaroo's pouch-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares. Spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the thing about a miracle is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't happen if you're just waiting for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is where it gets really amazing!\NAt least pretend to be interested! {Split this probably?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, I got a little hungry,\Nso I went to a convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I went up to the register...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:36.20,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,The change ended up being three yen more,\Nor something like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! It wasn't a boring miracle like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be 98 yen. {Name needs TSing}
Comment: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Buddha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an urna.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:24.81,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,Let's see, "an urna is the right-spiraled white hair\Nplaced on the forehead of the Buddha"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! That sure was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the thing about a miracle is you gotta\Nmake it happen yourself or there's no chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait! What the hell was that just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Great Buddha? Hey, Great Buddha?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:35.94,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,I'd give anything not to hear about your miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Robot. {Sign: Serious}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you absent yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.00,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,"No big deal"? But, you-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream about going to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought it was unreasonable that I had to\Ngo to school in both my dreams and in reality, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. Totally valid take.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\an8}Is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Isn't... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Damn it! Wota, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This time, try saying pizza ten times...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,May 15th, Wednesday. 12:40 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In response to Saginomiya's mysterious reason for her absence, Tanaka remarks "totally valid take"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's Ninomae!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, she always looks cool no matter when you look at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That uniquely girlish world that's adorned\Nwith pink and hearts and whatnot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That day of the entrance exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,if I hadn't had a fever running over 40 degrees\Nand diarrhea and nausea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and a headache and chicken pox and\Na strained back and sprained fingers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have been at this high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}See? Pizza, pizza, pizza, pizza, pizza, pizza, pizza!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the beginning of a grueling three years. {Sign pls i cant read kanji :Pensive:}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.55,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,As I steeled myself in preparation,\Non the day of the entrance ceremony... {That way? which way????????}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}1st-year Class Lists
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shiori Saginomiya
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Saginomiya...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Not to mention, we're in the same grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Saginomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a Miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well of course. That's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wonder if you can skip grades here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She was always the top of the class in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumour had it she was ranked in\Nthe top ten for the nationwide mock exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That Saginomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My future is sinking deep into the mud. {Are these basically unhearable blabberings necessary kek}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that I ran into her at this school,\Nwhere it's said that the average score
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,mirrors the intelligence of a four-year old is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She is this school's peerless genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.20,Default,TM,0,0,0,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mystifying aura has prevented me from speaking to you up till now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time for sure,\NI want to become acquainted with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it! I'll show you my best bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Roasted ham impression!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! That's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you never once let\Nthat poker face slip in middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be anticipating the next one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I got you covered!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That Saginomiya laughed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nerd, you try doing the roasted ham too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm not doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It can just be Iborian ham.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How's that any different than regular ham?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Also, it's not Iborian, it's Iberian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ibirian?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Iberian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Iburian?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Iberian!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore I have formulated a hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to become acquainted with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears essential that I appropriate\Nsomething like Tanaka's approach!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I will prove that I can solve\Nthis equation for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been one month and ten days since that day,\Nand I have continued my observation of Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I have yet to arrive at a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Have you ever smelled an ankle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's not something people normally smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna have some? It's a new flavor, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! H-here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's supposed to be shiitake mushrooms right? {drop "mushrooms?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}H-Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Eat! Bocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, thank you, Shortcake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Tanaka, you too-
Comment: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Chomp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! What are you, a gorilla?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop bullying Shortcake like that! Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shortcake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up. This is a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just having a bad dream, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You gotta properly apologize to Shortcake-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Shortcake! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump and overcome your sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on! You gotta jump! Shortcake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you're not gonna jump, then I'll jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll jump like crazy! I won't be restrained!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get away from here, Shortcake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you called me\Nmeans it's about that, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally come around\Nto liking high school girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But sorry, I'm not interested in you Mr. Sawatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of sushi toppings, I like a warasa yellow-tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Warasa is the label for promotional yellowtail\Nduring the mid-point of their growth,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and the even younger fish are called inada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Warasa aren't as gummy as inada are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The clear appeal of warasa comes from\Nthe umami of the exquisite layering of fat it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it is not possible for me\Nto ever like fully grown yellowtail or inada.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I have no idea what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's have a simpler conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grades have surpassed bombing and arrived at nuclear warhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,During the midterm exams, if you fail more than three subjects,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you will choose either to receive\None month of supplementary lessons,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,or you will get a crew cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen\Nhigh school girls with crew cuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they eating Choco Bats with a crew cut? {Where's the joke i dont get it}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.02,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,Can it at least be a 70% crew cut? {is this meant to be a fucking buzz cut? how can you have a 70% crew cut????}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh god! This is a girls emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When is Robot gonna get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she was coming,\Nbut she hasn't texted at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Should we get started for the time being?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh? Wait a sec. We're seriously gonna study?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that they get to study for tests\Nafter school with Saginomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me so deeply envious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're the one who said we should study\Nfor exams at a diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously that was just an\Njust an excuse, duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,An excuse to prevent you, Nerd,\Nfrom studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hit rock bottom together with these upcoming exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be the only one falling. Fall hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'll get motivated without a juicy cut of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Treat me, Nerd! I'll pay you back when I'm successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any money for somebody this hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,High-speed lip licking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Bathroom break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a huge shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I spending my time with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be at least one good thing about her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Think back. One good quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's none.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it like a Taco Bell shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop saying "shit" so loudly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha! {Holy fuck my audio just exploded}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an orange coffee cola cocoa\Ninfused soda with tabasco!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually drank it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The light...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you okay Nerd?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it! Nerd? Nerd?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikuchi! Kikuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Watcha drawing? Manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on, it's fine. So what?\NYou wanna become a manga artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Th-That's not it! It's not like I could become one anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way too tough a world to get into!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Obviously if you don't think you can, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you think you can, then you can, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's seaweed in her teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Nerd... Nerd!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Seaweed... The seaweed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What about seaweed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I-I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a minor flashback, that's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I totally went over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Thanks to that, I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm with her,\Nalthough it's frustrating to admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Were you remembering a past life\Nwhere you were seaweed or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure is funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This time it's spinach?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Spinach?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,After a prank gone too far against Kikuchi,\Nshe bares her teeth and grins like a chimpanzee...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're right. Lucky! Got me a snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Typical of Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Se-ri-ous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your math notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, make it all the subjects instead of just math. And the problem sheets too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm asking just in case, but if I do lend you them\Nwhat exactly would you be doing with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's obvious, I'll gratefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...bury them underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a mom joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Serious, I'll be copying your serious notes exactly as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when I fail all my subjects...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I definitely studied as much as I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{ARE THINGS NECESSARY HERE}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how I'll make my case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's far more efficient to simply study\Nthan to resort to cheap tricks like that you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you apply that motivation in a postive direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at my quiz results.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,, {\an8}I'd ask you not to underestimate my academic abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,English, 12%. Math, 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One percent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you possibly get grades this bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A royal flush!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've uncovered my plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, of course I'll pay the piper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How about two pieces of the Tanaka family's famous fried chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be dismissal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why in the world would I accept that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! How about three pieces then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You can put some lemon juice on it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is scaring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the quantity is not the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:12:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, thanks! I'll copy them and\Ngive them back to you ASAP, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about fried chicken is,\Nno matter how I look at it, it's tasty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and those of all ages like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it might as well be made\Ninto a worldwide currency or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we could finally achieve world peace, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I understand, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and take those and please leave me be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When I speak to Tanaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I get hit by a headache and this illusion\Nthat I'm losing my sense of equilibrium.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if those abnormal tendencies\Nare what piqued Saginomiya's interest, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-the thing about fried chicken is,\Nit's really delicious, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,e-everyone likes it and, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish it would be made into a worldwide currency or something! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you mean at all.
Comment: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The one thing I did figure out, however,\Nis that you are very much into fried chicken.
Comment: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,N...! N...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I've gone and done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally put Saginomiya off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\move(3102,1035,-1806,1034,23,6488)}She must think I'm an insane fried chicken fanatic who not only eats fried chicken for every meal of the day, but takes fried chicken baths, sleeps in a fried chicken bed and juggles fried chicken in her spare time! For sure! {WHAT THE FUCK IS THIS}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I must review my observation notes\Nto see what I did wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My observation notes were among the notes I ended up lending to Tanaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Absent today are Kujo and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninomae, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do? What to do? What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That notebook is all about Tanaka!
