Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap! Crap crap crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Given that it is Tanaka, there's no chance she would just let it go as if nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do, come on Ninomae, think!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\move(3404,1030,-1600,1030,29,7996)}As far as I can predict, based on her behaviour pattern she has 328 possible courses of action. Of course, she may easily skip over those and I can account for this diversion from my anticipation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is simply a biological study.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.67,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,Kanade? I brought some rice porridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's not as if I like Tanaka or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like I don't like her either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if it was between Tanaka and shoelaces,\NI would still prefer the shoelaces!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If it was Tanaka or soles,\Nthen the soles would still be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This fever has driven my daugher mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.68,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,However, by no means do I want to be stepped on\Nby soles or anything either. {I DISLIKE THIS LINE}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should stay home another day or two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a battle that I can't\Njust keep running away from, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:48.65,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,You've never won a battle while being this physically and mentally weak, my girl. {I FUCKING HATE THIS LINE BECAUSE I CANT THINK OF A GOOD WAY TO SAY "DAUGHTER"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't study for the tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I slept well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Tanaka. No matter when you arrive, I'm primed and ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right, please be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The test is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear your desks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Anyone not get an exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely she's not abandoning the battle, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she'd take it for sure and shamelessly fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Teacher, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That gives off the perception that I know everything about Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus, focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tana- huh? {Not really sure about how to do this type of line lmfao}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A crew cut is too lenient, so I went bald instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you worked super hard to lend these to me, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Serious, your notes were too serious you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the writing was super dense, the moment I opened them, I got sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only able to copy the first line of\Nancient literature. Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:16:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't see it! I'm so glad I live life seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, that hairstyle suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? You think so too?
