Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a typical view like this\Nlooks like it's shining...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining after school again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If we wait just a little, it looks like it'll let up. {random note, not sure what good practise is on these stutters. two capital letters or one cap one low?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll appreciate evening showers if they let me have moments like these with Saginomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot! I have to initiate some kind of conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It's really coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I keep an umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me in, let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. I have no clue what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what girls usually talk about at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,TV? Acting? Fashion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, I'm not in any of those loops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, this silence is causing a very awkward atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:16:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the perfect time for\Nthe Tanaka Observation Notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be some hint here on how to hold a conversation with Saginomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I not even have one conversation with the person I admire without relying on someone else? {breh}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's not going to stop anytime soon, is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Saginomiya, you'll get wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well of course I'll get wet. It is rain after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but... that's not it.\NWouldn't it be better to wait until it tapers off? {Is two sentences is here dece practise?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...decided on a three minute maximum wait time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Instant ramen also has that kind of limiter, right?
Comment: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, if you just wait five minutes,\Nthe rain will taper off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,See? The sky in the west is brightening up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that rain of all things is holding me up for even five minutes is annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, actually, I have an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So... please use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine! Come on, please take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I like getting wet with my clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! I've turned into some sort of high power-level degenerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The adhesion of cotton on skin just puts me on cloud nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh gods of rain, bless me with more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet again I've failed to acquaint myself with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,More! More adhesion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's definitely an interesting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not some kind of freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I just genuinely like getting wet\Nwith my clothes on, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I like how the wet cotton sticks to my skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our society would call someone like that a freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a bit of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like in anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to do that "Woosh!" thing so I climbed up here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really scary, and I'm getting goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been up here for four hours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I really need to pee and can't hold it at all, so what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My back's become a literal birds nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta do something before that bird comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,God, I'm unimportant. A minor character.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing here at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yamamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Well, I went to the hospital\Nand now I'm going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yamamoto, what are you doing here at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, I-I-I-I-I'm, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen me, I've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll unveil my secret to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on the lookout, you see. For them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's at least five of them,\Nuh no, s-seven of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Worst case, there's fourteen of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you truly have no idea then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well as long as my eagle eyes are watching from up here, there's no way they can make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it good practise to call the police or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not something you ordinary types would be able to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Those guys, the B-B-Blue Tree Bones are...
Comment: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Note: The clinic's name includes the kanji characters for:\N{\an7}Blue, Tree, Order, Bone, Clinic\N{\an8}Aoki Osteopathic Clinic {I would do something like "Sky Wood Orthopedic" here, Sky for Blue, Wood for Tree, Orthopedic for Bones.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frx0\fry0}Those guys are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Blue Tree Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even women and children don't escape their wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Serious, you should hurry up and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be fine on your own, Yamamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. Plus, I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it appears it has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My familiar, Spiritus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Spiritus?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, get going before they notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,V-Very well then.
Comment: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually wanted her to rescue me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a total idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously I would never\Nblindly accept a story like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you... You won't be able to get down-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can get down fine, just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That was like an anime! My dream came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, you just had to do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm gonna have to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My client, a certain organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,City?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a country, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Country?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. A country is waiting for me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,School is waiting for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Earlier, you were saying something\Nabout being an unimportant person, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're at least worth as much a knight from the Dragonia Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hire you if you're willing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Se-ri-ous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't given you that fried chicken as thanks for your notes yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.58,0:23:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I already had my lunch today, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say this makes up for it or anything but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fried chicken impression."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Serious? Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.32,0:23:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for video games at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be confiscating that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.70,0:23:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Saginomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for cultivated bacteria\Nat school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be confiscating that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind, but Sir,\Nplease handle them with extreme caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, they're troublesome bacteria\Nif they're exposed to air.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.36,0:23:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have them back.
